    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>With this widget you can show unlimited texts during the corresponding times to your visitors.</p>\n<p>Inspired by the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/time-based-greeting/\" rel=\"ugc\">time-based-greeting Plugin</a>, which gives you only the possibility to define exact four timeframes.<br />\nWith this improved Version you&#8217;re able to add unlimited timeframes.</p>\n<h3>Arbitrary section</h3>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Extract the zip file</li>\n<li>Drop the content in the wp-content/plugins/ or wp-content/mu-plugins directory of your WordPress installation</li>\n<li>Activate the Plugin from Plugins page</li>\n<li>Activate the widget by dropping it to an active sidebar under Appearance &gt; Widgets</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<p>If you are having a feature request or bug-reports for this plugin, <a href=\"https://github.com/carstingaxion/Better-time-based-greeting-Widget/issues/new\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">open an issue</a> on github.com.</p>\n",
        "changelog": "<p>1.0 (July 2012)<br />\n* first release</p>\n"
    },
